OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FSunny
OL,6,Fspells and a few showers Monday.
OL,7,FLargely dry with sunny spells Tuesday.
OL,8,FMostly cloudy with outbreaks of rain
OL,9,Fon Wednesday. Winds light Monday then
OL,10,Fbreezy on Tuesday and Wednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
